channel.title: First couple sigs
channel.description:
These are a couple sigs I actually had time to finish,not that experienced with ps yet.
Would love some constructive criticism.
[IMG]http://i143.photobucket.com/albums/r144/madoushi21/metcopy.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i143.photobucket.com/albums/r144/madoushi21/Frostiecopy.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i143.photobucket.com/albums/r144/madoushi21/startofsig.copy.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i143.photobucket.com/albums/r144/madoushi21/2ndbegincopy.jpg[/img]
Yes I know the text I did put on was for my very first sigs,before I knew text actually made it appealing or unappealing.
Will add text to the last two when I get better at doing it.
Last one is not completely yet finished,but meh.
Only have done like 2-3 other sigs besides these, I know they arent that great,trying to improve.
